{"tid":595500,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇小型sound bar推薦?","createTime":"2018-03-16T17:02:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T13:05:46.000Z","uid":3400,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"555fb2502c2d4c80496ef66ecccbc07d46dc765b","tid":595500,"uid":3400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T17:02:51.000Z","msg":"張電腦枱太細，冇乜地方可以放喇叭，局住用細隻既sound bar<br />\n預算2000，比電腦/PS4用，闊度最盡56cm，高度最盡7cm，有冇呢啲尺寸既sound bar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外我而家個駁法係電腦/PS4 &gt; DAC(Schiit Modi 2) &gt; AMP(Schiit Magni 3) &gt; 耳機<br />\n我見Magni 3有RCA output，係唔係可以駁落隻sound bar度，令到耳機同sound bar都有聲?"},{"pid":"2dc616780ea30ec654ecf912e46b1b728687072e","tid":595500,"uid":3400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T00:59:34.000Z","msg":"2000內好似冇乜細隻嘅sound bar，一係太長，一係有subwoofer<br />\n想預盤加到去3000選都係唔多，暫時見到嘅有<br />\nBose solo 5，bose soundlino mini 2，sony mt300(有subwiofer)<br />\n<br />\n如果唔用subwoofer會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b84c746a21ce8618f44f4ffe7d85d52f661bfa72","tid":595500,"uid":113625,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T08:39:25.000Z","msg":"EPC 果邊有人介紹隻 Philips Fidelio B1<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkepc.com/forum/viewthread.php?fid=25&amp;tid=2426044&amp;extra=page%3D3&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2Fforum%2Fviewthread.php%3Ffid%3D25%26tid%3D2426044%26extra%3Dpage%253D3%26page%3D1&d=dzibybXEdBHwvSxBIQK5X0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=1292800b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkepc.com/forum/viewthread.php?fid=25&amp;tid=2426044&amp;extra=page%3D3&amp;page=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://post76.hk/news/2016/08/%E7%B0%A1%E4%BE%BF%E5%BD%B1%E9%99%A2%E5%85%A9%E4%BB%B6%E9%A0%AD-%E8%BF%B7%E4%BD%A0%E5%96%87%E5%8F%AD%E7%B5%84%E5%90%88-philips-fidelio-b1-%E5%AF%A6%E6%B8%AC%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3